                    <p>Master linked list operations including insertion, deletion, reversal, and cycle detection. Practice with singly and doubly linked lists.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Start Lesson</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="badge">Week 3</span>
                        <span class="badge difficulty-medium">Intermediate</span>
                        <span>📅 Jan 29, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Stacks & Queues</h3>
                    <p>Understand LIFO and FIFO data structures. Implement stacks and queues, solve parentheses matching, and queue-based problems.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Coming Soon</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="badge">Week 4</span>
                        <span class="badge difficulty-medium">Intermediate</span>
                        <span>📅 Feb 5, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Binary Trees</h3>
                    <p>Explore tree traversals (inorder, preorder, postorder), tree construction, and common tree algorithms like height calculation.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Coming Soon</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="badge">Week 5</span>
                        <span class="badge difficulty-hard">Advanced</span>
                        <span>📅 Feb 12, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Binary Search Trees</h3>
                    <p>Learn BST properties, insertion, deletion, and search operations. Practice with BST validation and common BST problems.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Coming Soon</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="badge">Week 6</span>
                        <span class="badge difficulty-hard">Advanced</span>
                        <span>📅 Feb 19, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Graph Algorithms</h3>
                    <p>Master graph representations, BFS, DFS, shortest path algorithms (Dijkstra), and topological sorting.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Coming Soon</a>
